<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>We Received Your Message</title>
<style type="text/css">
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; color: #333; }
    table { border-collapse: collapse; }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        table[class="container"] { width: 95% !important; }
        td[class="header"] { font-size: 20px !important; padding: 15px !important; }
        td[class="content"] { padding: 15px !important; font-size: 16px !important; line-height: 22px !important; }
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" bgcolor="#f4f4f4">
    <tr><td height="30"></td></tr>
    <tr>
        <td align="center">
            <table class="container" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" bgcolor="#ffffff" style="border:1px solid #dddddd; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;">
                <tr>
                    <td class="header" bgcolor="#121212" style="padding:25px; text-align:center; color:#ffffff; font-size:24px; font-weight:bold;">
                        Hello {{name}},
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="content" style="padding:30px; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; color:#333;">
                        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                            Thank you for reaching out through my portfolio.
                        </p>
                        
                        <p>I have received your message and will review it shortly. I appreciate your time and will get back to you as soon as possible with a thoughtful response.</p>
                        
                        <h3 style="color:#121212; font-size:18px; margin-top:30px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 8px;">A recap of your message:</h3>
                        <div style="background-color:#f9f9f9; padding:15px; border-left:4px solid #FF3C3C; border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:{{email}}" style="color:#FF3C3C; text-decoration:none;">{{email}}</a></p>
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Subject:</strong> {{subject}}</p>
                            <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Message:</strong></p>
                            <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; font-style: italic;">"{{message}}"</p>
                        </div>

                        <p style="margin-top:35px; font-size: 16px;">Warm regards,<br/><strong style="color: #FF3C3C; font-size: 18px;">Maurya Soni</strong></p>

                        <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size:13px; color:#888; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 20px;">
                            <a href="https://portfolio-maurya-soni.vercel.app" target="_blank" style="color:#FF3C3C; text-decoration:none; font-weight: bold;">portfolio-maurya-soni.vercel.app</a>
                        </p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr><td height="30"></td></tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>